      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. It just feels like these clauses are designed to catch you off guard. Are there any specific ways these liabilities might sneak up on me? Like, is there anything 'under the surface' in a contract that could lead to these kinds of unexpected expenses or sudden legal issues?",
